Sorry about the screenshots, I was messing around with giving my self awps and I forgot to throw them away.


Hey guys.

I was releasing lots of versions of this map but now I'm releasing a final version. This map has only like 2 red lights in it and is now during the day.
It features two towers, a clearwall in the middle that you can shoot through, bunches of crates to hide behind, and a ladder to go up to the top.

I hope you enjoy this map.

Sincerely,

MattMcD1
